OL,6,GStrike action by members of the
OL,7,GNational Union of Journalists has
OL,8,Gaffected regional BBC TV news
OL,9,Gprogrammes for a second day.
OL,11,FThe 24-hour strike by BBC Local staff
OL,12,Fin England began at 11am yesterday and
OL,13,Faffected lunchtime, early evening and
OL,14,Flate-evening regional TV news
OL,15,Fprogrammes in most English regions, as
OL,16,Fwell as live output on many local radio
OL,17,Fstations.
