OL,6,FThe BBC said yesterday that it would
OL,7,Ftry to minimise disruption as much as
OL,8,Fpossible.
OL,10,FThe proposals for more local radio
OL,11,Fstations to share programming would
OL,12,F"see no overall reduction in staffing
OL,13,Flevels or local funding" and deliver
OL,14,F"even greater value to communities", a
OL,15,FBBC spokesperson said.
OL,17,FAll English regions managed to produce
OL,18,Ftheir own lunchtime updates at 1.30pm
OL,19,Ftoday.
